{"tid":1383681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪開始迷茫?  記住敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:35:31.000Z","uid":19817,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9646ddf2b8c3e0f171492b3fb442cadf8ab0b099","tid":1383681,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:52:22.000Z","msg":"又係打機時間<br />\n敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追。<br />\n呢四樣野咪就係BE WATER既精神<br />\n<br />\n已經有巴打開策略POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1383613/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1383613/page/1</a><br />\n記得要以唔會有人被捕為大前題去發夢<br />\n發夢大馬路對方準備好哂既話千其唔好肢體衝突, <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要令到佢地疲先可以打<br />\n暫時仲未做到敵疲我打, 大家要鬥智, 鬥完智先有得打</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敵人一天天爛下去，我們一天天好起來。<br />\n<br />\n在戰爭中學習戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n歷史是人民創造的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e178def5b256cb4062c6ed84515f3f165d97e1","tid":1383681,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:01:35.000Z","msg":"[解鎖遊戲新副本] 全城十八區幫老豆搵仔，百萬人探訪狗隻居所<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383671</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一齊討伐怪獸 幫幫手推</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d2e447b13d14630ed9e483bb6d16761f4f204d","tid":1383681,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:53:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"533123a6517502c102fbb3026e9441cd51ec25c7","tid":1383681,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T